<br>
1) I would think the offhand should be 12/22 (the red sword).<br>
2) Blue primary have 40 percent item haste, and 11/19 ratio. Now, my thought is, you should really think about if you want to replace your epic, but your epic should still be viable, and an end item if you so choose.<br>
3) Anyone have any experience regarding the aggro on the 2hs?  I know that primal 2hs seems to be an aggro magnet. Would think the warrior epic should be close if not more aggro even if the stats aren't quite as great.<br>
4) Nice idea about having the scabbard be a back slot item. Say, /shrug, 15 AC, and virtually no stats as it's not meant to be a back slot item, but as one that can be used in a pinch.<br>
<br>
As an aside, if the epic had been for a breastplate, would you have been happy? What stats do you think would have been acceptable?<br>
